never want to hang out with me all day.

127
00:09:05,878 --> 00:09:08,073
She sounds nice.

128
00:09:08,147 --> 00:09:11,878
- Hey.
- Oh. Hey there, you two.

129
00:09:11,951 --> 00:09:14,146
Hi, John.

130
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:16,984
Mrs. Solis.

131
00:09:17,089 --> 00:09:20,252
