Have fun.

135
00:09:34,907 --> 00:09:38,775
Doesn't it make you nervous?
A boy alone upstairs with Danielle?

136
00:09:38,878 --> 00:09:42,780
I don't worry about John. Both he and
Danielle are in the abstinence club.

137
00:09:46,953 --> 00:09:49,285
Coffee's a little hot.

138
00:09:55,494 --> 00:09:58,793
Susan was infuriated
by Paul's evasive answers.

139
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:04,395
She was convinced
he was deliberately hiding Zach

140
00:10:04,503 --> 00:10:07,666
and hiding the truth.

141
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:11,801
She hoped that finding one
would lead to the other.

142
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:18,179
To succed, Susan would
have to be evasive herself.

143
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:20,241
[Doorbell]

144
00:10:22,188 --> 00:10:25,589
- Susan. Long time no see.
- Mrs. Greenberg.

145
00:10:25,691 --> 00:10:30,594
Do you remember those two eggs
I let you borrow last Christmas?

146
00:10:30,696 --> 00:10:35,258
- I need those back.
- Gosh, honey, I'm fresh out.

147
00:10:35,368 --> 00:10:39,134
- But I could run to the store.
- Oh, forget about it.

148
00:10:39,205 --> 00:10:41,469
It's not that important.

149
00:10:41,540 --> 00:10:46,136
But since I'm here, do you still have
that hatchback sitting in your garage?

150
00:10:46,245 --> 00:10:49,578
- Can I borrow it tomorrow?
- You want to borrow my car?

151
00:10:49,649 --> 00:10:51,514
Just for a couple of hours.

152
00:10:51,584 --> 00:10:54,747
I'm not sure.
Do you know how to drive a stick?

153
00:10:54,854 --> 00:10:57,448
Yes, I think so. I learned in college.

154
00:10:57,556 --> 00:10:59,683
It's like riding a bike, right?

155
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:03,661
- I'm not sure, dear.
- It's just for a couple of hours.

156
00:11:03,763 --> 00:11:06,664
I let you borrow my eggs
for a whole year.

157
00:11:07,633 --> 00:11:11,967
I'm very pleased with the work
we've done in our sessions thus far.

158
00:11:12,071 --> 00:11:16,098
- We're making excellent progress.
- Thank you. I feel good about it.

159
00:11:16,175 --> 00:11:20,669
But there are a few areas of your
marriage we haven't covered yet.

160
00:11:20,746 --> 00:11:23,647
Oh, really? Like what?

161
00:11:25,151 --> 00:11:30,418
Um... I've told Dr. Goldfine
in our private sessions

162
00:11:30,523 --> 00:11:33,083
that I'm not happy with our sex life.

163
00:11:37,296 --> 00:11:41,926
And Rex feels that
when the two of you have intercourse,

164
00:11:42,068 --> 00:11:44,866
